    <!-- Cards Help / FAQ -->
    <string name="cards_help_no_update_title">Card information doesn\'t update</string>
    <string name="cards_help_no_update_answer">Card information is updated within &lt;b&gt;24h&lt;/b&gt;. Therefore you will only see the balance and activity from the previous day.</string>
    <string name="cards_help_validate_title">Can I validate my trip with the app on the bus?</string>
    <string name="cards_help_validate_answer">I wish, but no. SeviBus only shows card information but doesn\'t replace it. You must continue using your physical card when boarding the bus or tram.</string>
    <string name="cards_help_recharge_title">I recharged the card but the money doesn\'t appear</string>
    <string name="cards_help_recharge_answer">Online recharges will be effective within &lt;b&gt;24h&lt;/b&gt;, and after validating the card on a bus or tram. Until then, the previous balance will continue to appear.</string>
    <string name="cards_help_missing_trip_title">I used the card but the last trip doesn\'t appear</string>
    <string name="cards_help_missing_trip_answer">Card balance is updated within &lt;b&gt;24h&lt;/b&gt;. Therefore you will only see the balance and activity from the previous day.</string>
    <string name="cards_help_invalid_number_title">Card number is not valid</string>
    <string name="cards_help_invalid_number_answer">If your card is new, it might not be activated. You must validate it on a bus or tram, try again within 24 hours. If you\'ve already validated it and it still doesn\'t work, contact &lt;a href=\'mailto:sevibus@sloydev.com\'&gt;us&lt;/a&gt;.</string>
    <string name="cards_help_24h_delay_title">Why doesn\'t the information update until after 24 hours?</string>
    <string name="cards_help_24h_delay_answer">It\'s a technical limitation of Tussam, and there\'s nothing we can do from SeviBus. Remember that SeviBus is an independent app not related to Tussam.</string>
    <string name="cards_help_card_error_title">When I use my card on the bus or tram I get an error</string>
    <string name="cards_help_card_error_answer">From SeviBus we can\'t help you with problems using the card. Contact &lt;a href=\'https://www.tussam.es/contacto/\'&gt;Tussam&lt;/a&gt;.</string>

